# üåê Environment Variables

This file contains all environment variables needed for the HarvestPro NZ application across different environments.

## üìã Required Variables

### Supabase Configuration
```bash
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

### Sentry (Error Tracking)
```bash
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@xxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxx
```

### PostHog (Analytics)
```bash
VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=https://app.posthog.com
```

### Demo Mode (‚ö†Ô∏è Security-Sensitive)
```bash
# Set ONLY in development. Leave UNSET in staging/production.
# When set, the Demo tab appears on the Login page with pre-configured accounts.
# When unset, the Demo tab is hidden and NO credentials are in the JS bundle.
VITE_DEMO_PASSWORD=your-demo-password
```

### Firebase (Push Notifications) - Optional
```bash
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your-api-key
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your-sender-id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your-app-id
VITE_FIREBASE_VAPID_KEY=your-vapid-key
```

