## üÜò Troubleshooting

### "Environment variable not defined"
- Make sure you created `.env.local` from `.env.example`
- Restart dev server after adding variables
- Variables must start with `VITE_` to be exposed to the app

### "Sentry not capturing errors"
- Check `VITE_SENTRY_DSN` is set correctly
- Sentry is disabled in development mode by default
- Check browser console for Sentry initialization message

### "Supabase connection fails"
- Verify `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` and `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
- Check network tab for CORS errors
- Verify Supabase project is not paused

